value.0: Gorgons are bull-like creatures that guard their territory fiercely.  A typical gorgon stands over six feet tall at the shoulder and measures eight feet from snout to tail.  Although built like a bull, the gorgon is covered with metallic black scales and has silver horns.  Its eyes glow with an eerie green light, particularly when it grows angry. The gorgon's most dangerous weapon is its fearsome petrification breath attack.
Young Gorgon
